tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_circuit_parameters (
 circuit_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 circuit_name VARCHAR(255),
 gate_type VARCHAR(50),
 gate_params JSON,
 execution_time DOUBLE
)

CREATE TABLE circuit_parameters (
    param_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    circuit_id UUID REFERENCES quantum_circuits(circuit_id),
    parameter_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    parameter_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    parameter_value FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE circuit_parameters (
 parameter_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
 circuit_id INT,
 parameter_name VARCHAR(255),
 parameter_value FLOAT,
 FOREIGN KEY (circuit_id) REFERENCES quantum_circuits(circuit_id)
);

CREATE TABLE model_metrics (
 metric_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
 model_id INT,
 metric_name VARCHAR(255),
 metric_value FLOAT,
 FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES quantum_models(model_id)
);
